# Security Rules

## .env files

Never read, display, or reference `.env` files or their contents.
These files may contain secrets and sensitive credentials.

## Secrets and credentials

Do not include API keys, tokens, passwords, or other secrets in code or commit messages.
Do not read or reference credential files such as `.npmrc`, `credentials.json`, or similar.
